headline: Why Zebra (ZBRA) Stock Is Up Today
summary: Shares of enterprise data capture company Zebra Technologies (NASDAQ:ZBRA) jumped 4.5% in the afternoon session after the company announced it completed its acquisition of Elo Touch Solutions.
